reviewText: Have been a follower of this show for years and was delighted to get the entire set for some of the shows I had missed.
Love this series.  Very intertaing. Love it. Love it. ya ya ya ya ya ya ya. Action packed and intresting.
Love Love Love this series....it was ashame to have cancelled this.  I bought this to watch it over and over again.  My very favorite CSI series.
WHEAT BELLY... I LOST 60 POUNDS IN 12 MONTHS AND STILL FOLLOW GUIDELINES. DROPPED FRON 255 TO 195. 44 TO 38 PANTS AND XL TO L. SHIRTS. DONATED 70 POUNDS OF CLOTHING TO RED CROSS. ABOUT SAYS IT ALL!
Great to be able to watch all the season shows, one right after another if I want, when I want. It was cheaper to buy the bunch, than singly
If you are a CSI fan this set is a must buy. I especially love the "commentaries" as wells as the behind the scene featurettes. Check it out!!
